<geoCoordinate id="EE065DD9FFB4FFD068EFFED5FB7B5B2A" box="[1180,1245,262,286]" degrees="2" direction="south" minutes="23" orientation="latitude" pageId="3" pageNumber="599" precision="925" value="-2.3833332">S2 23</geoCoordinate>
. Tube length 105, anal setae 100. Fore wing length 560. Antennal segments III–VIII length 53, 55, 55, 48, 42, 25.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B8D3B1EFFB4FFD06CB4FE9DFB025B52" blockId="3.[151,1437,154,1114]" box="[199,1188,334,358]" pageId="3" pageNumber="599">
<emphasis id="B946E70CFFB4FFD06CB4FE9DFEDD5B51" box="[199,379,334,358]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="599">Male microptera</emphasis>
